@EliHeathMusic It sounds like an FFT time-stretch and smear. It's a bit surprising to hear on a pop(ish) record, actually. Cool, though.

I'm not sure which plugins today are doing that kind of FFT transformation, but if I had to do it I'd use these Michael Norris SoundMagic Spectral plugins. They're old, have zero GUI, and are probably still a bit buggy, but they'll do the trick.

https://www.michaelnorris.info/software/soundmagic-spectral

